    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Little Brave 是一款浸涛式的 2D 横版动作冒险游戏，讲述一个名叫奇利（Keely）小男孩的故事。准备好迎接激动人心的冒险吧。揭示古老传说的秘密，在旅途中获得勇气与力量！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724300/extras/4718696a0576a67327261e74400aa3e0.poster.avif?t=1748472293\" width=800 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724300/extras/4718696a0576a67327261e74400aa3e0.webm?t=1748472293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724300/extras/4718696a0576a67327261e74400aa3e0.mp4?t=1748472293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >奇利生活在一个曾经充满神秘力量的世界。然而，一场可怕的咒符扭曲了这些神秘地方。奇利梦想着踏上探索禁地秘密和第一守卫者秘密的旅途。当命运给予他这样一次机会…</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>精心设计的地点和棘手的谜语</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t探索禁地；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t解谜;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t克服险恶的陷阱;</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724300/extras/15285ca08449f2669d97050faf32bf6e.poster.avif?t=1748472293\" width=800 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724300/extras/15285ca08449f2669d97050faf32bf6e.webm?t=1748472293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724300/extras/15285ca08449f2669d97050faf32bf6e.mp4?t=1748472293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>有效技能与给力的敌人AI</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t综合使用近战武器、远程攻击和神秘力量；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对抗险恶的敌人;</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724300/extras/b025ee10163cfd5a2ef9e8dc238952c6.poster.avif?t=1748472293\" width=800 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724300/extras/b025ee10163cfd5a2ef9e8dc238952c6.webm?t=1748472293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724300/extras/b025ee10163cfd5a2ef9e8dc238952c6.mp4?t=1748472293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>充满秘密和故事的冒险故事</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t找到失落魔力的最后碎片；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t打败强大的守护者;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t揭示传奇旧日的秘密；</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724300/extras/49c484fcfa6b2a84a3899a72e6236896.poster.avif?t=1748472293\" width=800 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724300/extras/49c484fcfa6b2a84a3899a72e6236896.webm?t=1748472293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724300/extras/49c484fcfa6b2a84a3899a72e6236896.mp4?t=1748472293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在旅途中积累勇气</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t找到并拯救奇利的小妹韦卡；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t战胜禁地中的怪物.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724300/extras/644482139a0d553bfa3da8638fc353bf.poster.avif?t=1748472293\" width=800 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724300/extras/644482139a0d553bfa3da8638fc353bf.webm?t=1748472293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724300/extras/644482139a0d553bfa3da8638fc353bf.mp4?t=1748472293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
